title: GoPro Awards: Forward Motion With Nenad Pagonis
description:
Join world championship kickboxer Nenad Pagonis for a unique stroll down Dunavska Street, one of the oldest streets in Novi Sad, Serbia.

Captured, edited and submitted by GoPro Awards recipient, Zoran Marinković.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music
Bear Dance "Slow Magic"
